+ Class Properties

++ Public

* Solar_Uri::$fragment -- The fragment portion (e.g., "#subsection").

* Solar_Uri::$host -- The host specification (e.g., 'example.com').

* Solar_Uri::$info -- Path info elements after the script name (from $_SERVER['PATH_INFO']).

* Solar_Uri::$pass -- The password, if any.

* Solar_Uri::$path -- The path portion (e.g., 'path/to/index.php').

* Solar_Uri::$port -- The port number (e.g., '80').

* Solar_Uri::$query -- Query string elements split apart into an array.

* Solar_Uri::$scheme -- The scheme (e.g. 'http' or 'https').

* Solar_Uri::$user -- The username, if any.

++ Protected

* Solar_Uri::$_config -- User-provided configuration values.

++ Private

None.